trans-unit.source: Contains a strongly typed collection of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> objects.
The <xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElementCollection> class is used to work with a collection of <xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement> objects.
Creates a new <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElementCollection"></xref>.
Adds a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to add.
Removes all <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> objects from the collection.
Returns a <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref> that indicates whether a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> with the specified key exists in the collection.
The key of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to find in the collection.
`true` if the collection contains a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> with the specified key; otherwise, `false`.
Copies the elements from the collection to an array, starting at a particular index of the array.
An array of type <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to which to copy the contents of the collection.
The zero-based index in Array at which copying begins.
Returns the zero-based index of a specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> in the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to find in the collection.
The zero-based index of the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref>, or -1 if the element was not found in the collection.
Gets or sets the element at a specified index in the collection.
The zero-based index into the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> that exists at the specified index.
Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> that has the specified key in the collection.
The key of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to get or set in the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> with the specified key.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> with the specified key was not found in the collection.
Removes a specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> from the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to remove from the collection.
Removes the element at the specified index in the collection.
The zero-based index of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to remove from the collection.
Removes the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> with the specified key from the collection.
The key of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElement"></xref> to be removed from the collection.
